  m_Name: GSWGA_Course_1_Final_Assessment_Q10
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionData
  question: 'A customer service team is introducing a new chatbot and wants to give
    it a catchy name that users will remember. A developer on the team prompts the
    generative AI tool to provide a list of possible names.

    What generative
    AI task is the team performing?'
  answers:
  - Problem solving
  - Personalization
  - Content creation
  - Idea generation
  maxSelections: 1
  correctAnswerIndices: 03000000
  correctMessage: A task that generative AI tools excel at is creating ideas such
    as product names, titles, themes, or concepts.
  incorrectMessage: Not quite. Consider that the team wants to explore some possible
    names for the next chatbot.
